{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "core:dlg_elder_first_meet",
      "npcId": "core:npc_qingyun_elder",
      "name": "青云长老初见",
      "priority": 100,
      "once": true,
      "condition": {
        "minAffinity": 0,
        "relationLevel": ["stranger", "acquaintance"]
      },
      "startNodeId": "n1",
      "tags": ["greeting", "lore"],
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "n1",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「年轻人，初入修途，前路漫漫。你可有什么想要请教的？」",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "🙏 请长老指点修行之道。",
              "nextNodeId": "n2",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": 5 }
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "💰 有没有什么好处？",
              "nextNodeId": "n3",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": -2 }
            },
            {
              "id": "c3",
              "text": "👋 多谢，告辞。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "n2",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「好，就凭你这份心性。这两枚回灵丹送你，修炼之余用得上。记住：修行如逆水行舟，不进则退。」",
          "effects": {
            "giveItems": [{ "itemId": "core:hp_pill", "count": 2 }]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "n3",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「哼，修行之路若只图好处，迟早走错路。去吧，自己好好想想。」"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "core:dlg_elder_realm2_advice",
      "npcId": "core:npc_qingyun_elder",
      "name": "青云长老突破建议",
      "priority": 80,
      "once": true,
      "condition": {
        "minAffinity": 20,
        "minRealm": 2,
        "relationLevel": ["friend", "close_friend", "soulmate"]
      },
      "startNodeId": "n1",
      "tags": ["lore", "gift"],
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "n1",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「嗯，你的修为有所精进，已入金丹之境。接下来的路更加艰难，须以心志坚如磐石。」",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "🙏 请长老赐教。",
              "nextNodeId": "n2",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": 3 }
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "💪 晚辈自有把握！",
              "nextNodeId": "n3",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": -1 }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "n2",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「善。这几枚筑基丹虽不稀罕，但对你突破下一境界或有助益。切记，修行不可急功近利。」",
          "effects": {
            "giveItems": [{ "itemId": "core:spirit_stone_shard", "count": 3 }],
            "expChange": 200
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "n3",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「年轻气盛……也罢，碰壁之后自会明白。去吧。」"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "core:dlg_herb_master_trade",
      "npcId": "core:npc_herb_master",
      "name": "灵药谷药师论药",
      "priority": 50,
      "cooldown": 12,
      "condition": {
        "minAffinity": 10,
        "relationLevel": ["acquaintance", "friend", "close_friend", "soulmate"]
      },
      "startNodeId": "n1",
      "tags": ["trade", "lore"],
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "n1",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「嗯？你来了。最近采到了不少灵草，要不要聊聊灵药之道？」",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "🌿 请教灵药知识。",
              "nextNodeId": "n2",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": 3 }
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "💊 有没有多余的灵草分我些？",
              "nextNodeId": "n3",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": -1 }
            },
            {
              "id": "c3",
              "text": "👋 下次再来请教。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "n2",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「灵药讲究天时地利，采摘时辰至关重要。这些灵草是我多余的，你拿去练练手吧。」",
          "effects": {
            "giveItems": [{ "itemId": "core:spirit_herb", "count": 2 }]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "n3",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「哼，灵草可不是随便能要的。不过看在你还算有诚意的份上，给你一株吧。」",
          "effects": {
            "giveItems": [{ "itemId": "core:spirit_herb", "count": 1 }]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "core:dlg_beast_hunter_challenge",
      "npcId": "core:npc_beast_hunter",
      "name": "猎妖人切磋",
      "priority": 50,
      "cooldown": 6,
      "condition": {
        "minAffinity": 30,
        "relationLevel": ["friend", "close_friend", "soulmate"],
        "minRealm": 2
      },
      "startNodeId": "n1",
      "tags": ["combat"],
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "n1",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「嘿！看你实力不错，要不来过两招？别怕，点到为止！」",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "⚔️ 好！来就来！",
              "nextNodeId": "n2",
              "effects": {
                "affinityChange": 5,
                "triggerCombatNpcId": "core:npc_beast_hunter"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "🙅 今天身体不适，改日再战。",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": -1 }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "n2",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「哈哈！痛快！那就开始吧——」"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "core:dlg_market_chen_gossip",
      "npcId": "core:npc_market_chen",
      "name": "陈掌柜打听消息",
      "priority": 40,
      "cooldown": 6,
      "condition": {
        "minAffinity": 10,
        "relationLevel": ["acquaintance", "friend", "close_friend", "soulmate"]
      },
      "startNodeId": "n1",
      "tags": ["lore", "gossip"],
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "n1",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「嘿嘿，又来啦？最近打听到了些有趣的消息，要不要听听？」",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "👂 愿闻其详。",
              "nextNodeId": "n2",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": 2 }
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "💰 消息值多少钱？",
              "nextNodeId": "n3"
            },
            {
              "id": "c3",
              "text": "👋 今天没心情。",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": -1 }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "n2",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「听说北边荒原深处最近妖兽异动频繁，可能有什么宝物出世。你若有胆量，不妨去看看。不过可别说是我告诉你的！」",
          "effects": {
            "expChange": 50,
            "setDialogueFlag": { "key": "chen_gossip_heard", "value": true }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "n3",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「哈哈，做生意就是要精打细算。算了，不收你钱——下次多在我店里买点东西就行。」",
          "nextNodeId": "n2"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "core:dlg_wanderer_li_mystery",
      "npcId": "core:npc_wanderer_li",
      "name": "散修李无名的秘密",
      "priority": 60,
      "once": true,
      "condition": {
        "minAffinity": 30,
        "relationLevel": ["friend", "close_friend", "soulmate"],
        "minRealm": 3
      },
      "startNodeId": "n1",
      "tags": ["lore", "mystery"],
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "n1",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「……你的修为已经到了这一步。也罢，有些事，是时候告诉你了。」",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "🤔 什么事？",
              "nextNodeId": "n2",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": 5 }
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "🙅 不想知道。",
              "effects": { "affinityChange": -3 }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "n2",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「我一直在寻找上古遗迹的线索。传说在极北之地，有一处被封印的洞天福地，内藏仙人遗宝。」",
          "nextNodeId": "n3"
        },
        {
          "id": "n3",
          "type": "npc_talk",
          "text": "「以你现在的实力，或许可以一试。记住这个名字——'玄天秘境'。日后若有机会，你自会明白。」",
          "effects": {
            "setDialogueFlag": { "key": "li_secret_revealed", "value": true },
            "setNpcFlag": { "key": "revealed_secret", "value": true },
            "expChange": 300
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "idleChat": {
    "gentle": [
      "「修行之路，贵在坚持。」",
      "「心怀善念，自有天助。」",
      "「前辈有何指教？」",
      "「今日天色不错，适合修炼。」"
    ],
    "cold": [
      "「……」",
      "「无事勿扰。」",
      "「你还不够资格。」",
      "「走吧。」"
    ],
    "hot_tempered": [
      "「废话少说！有事快讲！」",
      "「哼，又来了。」",
      "「要切磋就痛快点！」",
      "「别磨磨蹭蹭的！」"
    ],
    "cunning": [
      "「嘿嘿，有好东西吗？」",
      "「做生意讲个诚信。」",
      "「这笔买卖不亏。」",
      "「你有什么想买的？」"
    ],
    "righteous": [
      "「正义之道，不可偏废。」",
      "「守护弱者，乃修士本分。」",
      "「你心中有正气。」",
      "「行善积德，天道酬勤。」"
    ],
    "mysterious": [
      "「天机不可泄露……」",
      "「或许……某日你会明白。」",
      "「有缘再见。」",
      "「此中有深意，你自己体会吧。」"
    ]
  }
}
